# Concurrency

- async/await; Task for structured concurrency
- @MainActor for UI; nonisolated for services that run off main
- Task.checkCancellation() in long loops
- Avoid Task.detached; avoid MainActor.run when possible
- Sendable for types crossing actor boundaries
